                "invention-title": [
                    "HAIR CLEANSER COMPOSITION",
                    "毛髪洗浄剤組成物"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "To provide a hair cleanser composition which has excellent coacervate formation ability, is easily discharged from a pump, has an appropriate viscosity of easily foaming during washing and has low temperature stability capable of maintaining a transparent appearance even at a low temperature.SOLUTION: There is provided a hair cleanser composition which comprises a component (A): 1 to 20 mass% of a surfactant represented by the following formula (1), a component (B): 1 to 20 mass% of an amphoteric surfactant, a component (C): 0.03 to 3 mass% of a cationized polymer and a component (D): 0.001 to 1.5 mass% of β-alanine and/or a derivative thereof, wherein the mass ratio ((A)/(B)) is 0.2 to 4 and the mass ratio ((A)/(D)) is 15 to 300. (R1CO represents an aliphatic acyl group having 8 to 22 carbon atoms, R2 represents a hydrogen atom or a linear or branched-chain alkyl group having 1 to 4 carbon atoms which may have one hydroxyl group, M represents an alkali metal atom, a 1/2 alkaline earth metal atom or an organic ammonium.)SELECTED DRAWING: None"
                },
                {
                    "p": "【課題】コアセルベートの形成能に優れるとともに、ポンプからの吐出がし易く、洗浄時に泡立て易い適度な粘度を有し、低温時においても透明な外観を維持できる低温安定性を有する毛髪洗浄剤組成物の提供。【解決手段】成分（Ａ）：下記式（１）で表される界面活性剤を１～２０質量％、成分（Ｂ）：両性界面活性剤を１～２０質量％、成分（Ｃ）：カチオン化ポリマーを０．０３～３質量％、成分（Ｄ）：β－アラニンおよび／またはその誘導体を０．００１～１．５質量％含有し、質量比（（Ａ）／（Ｂ））が０．２～４であり、かつ質量比（（Ａ）／（Ｄ））が１５～３００である毛髪洗浄剤組成物。【化１】TIFF2024012130000014.tif2383（Ｒ１ＣＯは炭素数８～２２の脂肪族アシル基を示し、Ｒ２は水素原子、または１つの水酸基を有していてもよい炭素数１～４の直鎖もしくは分岐鎖のアルキル基を示し、Ｍはアルカリ金属、１／２アルカリ土類金属、または有機アンモニウムを示す。）【選択図】なし"
                }
